title: Agnus Dei
verses:
Alleluia Alleluluia 
for the Lord almighty reigns 
Alleluia Alleluluia 
Holy holy are you Lord God Almighty 
Worthy is the lamb 
Worthy is the lamb 
Holy holy are you Lord God Almighty

Worthy is the lamb 
Worthy is the lamb 
You are holy holy 
Are you lamb 
Worthy is the lamb 
You are holy holy 
You are holy holy
